# Requirements Directory

This directory contains software requirements, specs, and tickets.

## Naming Convention

`[ticket-id]-description.md` or `YYYY-MM-DD-description.md`

Examples:
- `ENG-1234-user-authentication.md`
- `2025-12-20-api-rate-limiting.md`

## Template

```markdown
# [Feature Name]

## Overview
[Brief description of the requirement]

## User Story
As a [user type], I want [goal] so that [benefit].

## Acceptance Criteria
- [ ] Criteria 1
- [ ] Criteria 2
- [ ] Criteria 3

## Technical Notes
[Any technical constraints or considerations]

## Dependencies
- [Dependency 1]
- [Dependency 2]

## Priority
[Critical / High / Medium / Low]
```

## Workflow

1. Create requirement in `thoughts/shared/requirements/`
2. Run `/create_plan` referencing the requirement
3. Plan is created in `thoughts/shared/plans/`
4. Run `/implement_plan` to execute
